author: doll
msg: All responses are now wrapped in an envelope. So instead of just getting a person as a response you get a person wrapped in an entry element.
To do this I had RestfulCollection and DataCollection extend ResponseItem instead of being composed by it. There is also now a RestfulItem which allows a single item response.
This change is large only because the interface changes touch everything...
